OL,3,C'There's fresh energy around Wales
OL,4,Cunder Craig Bellamy', says Connor
OL,5,CRoberts
OL,7,FConnor Roberts says there is "fresh
OL,8,Fenergy" and "excitement" around Wales
OL,9,Fafter telling team mates to expect a
OL,10,Ffar different set-up under new boss
OL,11,FCraig Bellamy.
OL,13,FThere was a first glimpse today of
OL,14,FWales' new look coaching staff under
OL,15,FBellamy.
OL,17,FIt's as Wales' men continue their
OL,18,Fpreparations for their opening Nations
OL,19,FLeague game on Friday against Turkey
OL,20,Fin Cardiff.
