OL,3,C'There's fresh energy around Wales
OL,4,Cunder Craig Bellamy', says Connor
OL,5,CRoberts
OL,7,FBellamy was Vincent Kompany's
OL,8,Fassistant as Burnley romped to the
OL,9,FChampionship title by accumulating 101
OL,10,Fpoints in the 2022-23 season before
OL,11,Fbeing relegated from the Premier
OL,12,FLeague.
OL,14,FKompany left on the back of relegation
OL,15,Fto take charge of Bayern Munich this
OL,16,Fsummer, while Bellamy was appointed
OL,17,FWales manager following the dismissal
OL,18,Fof Rob Page.
OL,20,F"You can see there is a new energy
OL,21,Faround the place," Roberts said.
