OL,3,C'There's fresh energy around Wales
OL,4,Cunder Craig Bellamy', says Connor
OL,5,CRoberts
OL,7,F"Everyone is excited to see what a
OL,8,FCraig Bellamy team looks like, how
OL,9,Fthey play.
OL,11,F"It's the same with the players. We
OL,12,Fall love playing for Wales and we all
OL,13,Fhave to impress the boss by tuning in
OL,14,Fto his ideas and want to be part of
OL,15,Fsomething successful.
OL,17,F"I know for a fact when there were
OL,18,Fwhispers of the gaffer coming in, some
OL,19,Fpeople asked questions ` 'was it
OL,20,Fright, was it not?'.
