OL,3,C'There's fresh energy around Wales
OL,4,Cunder Craig Bellamy', says Connor
OL,5,CRoberts
OL,7,FBellamy, who captained Wales during a
OL,8,F78-cap career between 1998 and 2013,
OL,9,Fmakes his managerial bow against Euro
OL,10,F2024 quarter-finalists Turkey in
OL,11,FCardiff on Friday.
OL,13,FWales then head to Montenegro three
OL,14,Fdays later for the second of their
OL,15,FGroup B4 fixtures.
OL,17,FPlayers have spoken of how level of
OL,18,Fdetail ` both on the pitch and in
OL,19,Fmeeting rooms ` has risen during the
OL,20,Ftwo days that the squad has been in
OL,21,Fcamp at their Vale of Glamorgan base.
