OL,3,C'There's fresh energy around Wales
OL,4,Cunder Craig Bellamy', says Connor
OL,5,CRoberts
OL,7,F"I think me and all the other boys in
OL,8,Fthe squad knew that was coming. With a
OL,9,Fnew coach it's always going to be like
OL,10,Fthat and, with Craig and his staff,
OL,11,Fit's even more so than any normal
