OL,3,C'There's fresh energy around Wales
OL,4,Cunder Craig Bellamy', says Connor
OL,5,CRoberts
OL,7,FBellamy had a hugely successful top-
OL,8,Fflight club career, winning honours at
OL,9,FCeltic and Liverpool and also playing
OL,10,Ffor Newcastle and Manchester City
OL,11,Famong others.
OL,13,FBut the former striker never
OL,14,Frepresented Wales at a major
OL,15,Ftournament and has admitted to being
OL,16,Fenvious of players ` many of whom are
OL,17,Fin his first squad ` who went on to do
OL,18,Fso at Euro 2016, Euro 2020 and the
OL,19,F2022 World Cup.
